For IIT’s intricate mathematical formulations to stand, more empirical data is needed to substantiate \( \Phi \) as a consciousness marker, particularly in non-biological systems. Currently, IIT lacks concrete verification for its predictions beyond theoretical assertions, leaving its scientific standing shaky.

